类 RFIDWithISO14443B_mtk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.team.mtk.deviceapi.RFIDBase_mtk

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IRFIDBase, IRFIDWithISO14443B

    public class RFIDWithISO14443B_mtk
extends RFIDBase_mtk
implements IRFIDWithISO14443B
    RFID模块ISO14443B协议操作类
    RFID module ISO14443B protocol operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before using.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directoy \libs\armeabi\ then module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 RFIDBase_mtk.init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 RFIDBase_mtk.free() 关闭设备
    3. call RFIDBase_mtk.init() to switch on the device before operating, call RFIDBase_mtk.free() to switch off the device after using.

    作者:
    liuruifeng
